name: shit my mexican family has said - cold edition #01
description:
to this day, my mother still claims walking barefoot on any floor that is not carpet causes sickness. in fact, if i get sick or my son gets sick her first response is always "see, i told you. this is your fault for not wearing socks." 

it took me a lot longer than i'd like to admit to get over my irrational fear of going outside in the cold with wet hair. i was told my mouth may turn sideways and was late to things sometimes because i was blow drying my hair. still no idea where that one came from.
